wordpressPost.title: Weird polka
wordpressPost.content: I don't know what is wrong with Weird Al but he won't stop polkaing good music. The embedded video is of a collage of things he polkad in one of his songs matched synchronised perfectly with the originals. It's something you have to love, just have to.
